1
00:00:16,040 --> 00:00:16,840
Jia Yu.

2
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:17,600
What happened?

3
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:18,040
Hurry.

4
00:00:18,040 --> 00:00:18,600
Three kids

5
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:19,600
were taken away by a black car.

6
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:20,120
Go.

7
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:20,720
Kids?

8
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:21,080
Yes.

9
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:22,040
Hao Qing asked me to save them.

10
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:23,000
Leave it and go.

11
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:31,560
It's you.

12
00:01:31,560 --> 00:01:33,160
Why?

13
00:01:34,600 --> 00:01:35,720
I arranged the whole thing

14
00:01:35,720 --> 00:01:36,640
to show you.

15
00:01:37,640 --> 00:01:38,840
Including the kidnapping.

16
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,560
You're testing me.

17
00:01:45,960 --> 00:01:47,360
You never trusted me,

18
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:47,960
right?

19
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,480
You betrayed my brother.

20
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,840
Why should I trust you?

21
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,240
Yes.

22
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,920
But I never wanted him to die.

23
00:02:03,920 --> 00:02:05,120
Never.

24
00:02:11,560 --> 00:02:12,520
When I was a kid,

25
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,560
I was taken from the orphanage by J,

26
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:20,040
trained,

27
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:20,680
and reformed.

28
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:23,000
I lost my name,

29
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:24,520
my past,

30
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,520
and even

31
00:02:27,600 --> 00:02:29,240
my humanity.

32
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,640
I was assigned to Hao Feng's side

33
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:33,600
to monitor him.

34
00:02:33,600 --> 00:02:34,400
I found

35
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,400
we were actually the same kind of people.

36
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,760
We both live for others.

37
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:42,600
But Hao Feng,

38
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,640
he knows what he's doing.

39
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,120
He has his own grand ambitions.

40
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,000
Hao Feng was the first person

41
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,400
to treat me as a friend.

42
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,200
How could I bear to hurt him?

43
00:03:07,680 --> 00:03:08,560
Just now,

44
00:03:08,560 --> 00:03:10,000
a secret ledger

45
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,800
purportedly from within the orphanage

46
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,600
has been circulating online.

47
00:03:12,600 --> 00:03:14,480
There is a huge discrepancy

48
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,360
between the donations claimed

49
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,840
[is far less than]

50
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:18,280
[the actual amount received,]

51
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,480
[suspected of donation fraud.]

52
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,560
[We will continue to follow up.]

53
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,040
Have some water.

54
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:32,120
J won't let these children go.

55
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:34,480
We have to find a way to stop them.

56
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,560
Don't worry.

57
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:37,680
I've already exposed the orphanage's

58
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:38,400
scandal.

59
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,720
They won't dare to act rashly for now.

60
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,920
What are your plans next?

61
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,840
The exposure of the orphanage

62
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,240
will inevitably involve

63
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,280
Zhen Era Fund.

64
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,880
Zhen Era's most urgent task now

65
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,640
is to transfer the money from the accounts.

66
00:03:52,040 --> 00:03:53,000
There's one more thing.

67
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,720
Mo Wen has discovered our plan.

68
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:07,000
The account book has been copied.

69
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,320
Remember what I told you.

70
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:13,640
Keep your mouth shut.

71
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,880
If necessary,

72
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,279
the boss will give you new instructions.

73
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,519
You're not from Zhen Era.

74
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:23,240
You're here to fight against Zhen.

75
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,040
For the past ten years,

76
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,760
I knew the orphanage was just a cover

77
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,400
for Zhen to pretend to be a philanthropist.

78
00:04:34,080 --> 00:04:35,680
But I'm just an ordinary person.

79
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,120
I don't have the ability

80
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,400
or courage to fight against him.

81
00:04:44,280 --> 00:04:46,200
Besides, my sister needs money for her illness.

82
00:04:50,280 --> 00:04:51,920
You approached me indirectly

83
00:04:52,960 --> 00:04:54,240
because of this, right?

84
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:57,160
What else do you know?

85
00:05:02,080 --> 00:05:02,840
It's the most painful thing

86
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:04,520
when a person can't

87
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,280
confront his conscience.

88
00:05:11,800 --> 00:05:12,720
I'll take a gamble.

89
00:05:14,200 --> 00:05:15,480
I bet you can take him down.

90
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:20,040
I only have one request.

91
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,880
Please save my sister.

92
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:24,520
Her illness is really...

93
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:25,280
I'll help you.

94
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:29,520
I'll do my best

95
00:05:29,520 --> 00:05:30,600
to protect you two.

96
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,200
Thank you.

97
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,520
You really look like Huai Yuan.

98
00:05:52,880 --> 00:05:54,040
I hope that child

99
00:05:55,080 --> 00:05:56,440
is doing well now.

100
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,600
Zhen Shida will find out

101
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,520
that Mo Wen exposed the account books.

102
00:06:02,520 --> 00:06:03,560
I promised her

103
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,240
to protect her sisters.

104
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,840
I have already asked Zhang Xiaoshao

105
00:06:07,840 --> 00:06:08,920
to settle them down.

106
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,040
As for Zhen Shida,

107
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,400
I have a way to stop him.

108
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:14,920
I said

109
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,360
I won't sacrifice the innocent

110
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,400
for my plan.

111
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,520
The cage is ready.

112
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:25,720
Next, we just wait for Zhen Shida

113
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,840
to walk right into it.

114
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,240
[A secret ledger,]

115
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:34,080
[allegedly from within the orphanage,]

116
00:06:34,080 --> 00:06:34,960
[has been leaked online.]

117
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,840
[The Zhen Era Foundation claims to]

118
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:37,520
[have donated funds.]

119
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:42,240
Didn't I tell you

120
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:43,680
not to bother me unless it's urgent?

121
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,080
Boss Zhen,

122
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,320
losing your temper like this

123
00:06:48,320 --> 00:06:49,480
isn't good for your health.

124
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,680
Thank you for your concern,

125
00:06:51,200 --> 00:06:52,680
but don't bother.

126
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:54,840
Speak up,

127
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:56,840
what do you need from me?

128
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,560
I owe you a favor, don't I?

129
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:03,760
So?

130
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:06,240
This time,

131
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:11,280
I'm not here to repay you.

132
00:07:11,280 --> 00:07:12,000
It's your turn

133
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,200
to do me a favor.
